OL,3,CMan dies after drive-by shooting in
OL,4,CBrixton
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a 25-year-old man died
OL,8,Fafter a drive-by shooting at a
OL,9,Fbarbecue in south London at the
OL,10,Fweekend.
OL,12,FFour people were injured after shots
OL,13,Fwere fired from a vehicle in
OL,14,FColdharbour Lane, Brixton, just after
OL,15,F1am on Saturday.
OL,17,FKeanu Taylor, 25, has since died in
OL,18,Fhospital of his wounds, the
OL,19,FMetropolitan Police said.
