OL,3,CMan dies after drive-by shooting in
OL,4,CBrixton
OL,6,FThree others, aged 21, 47 and 70, who
OL,7,Fwere hurt in the shooting do not have
OL,8,Flifethreatening or life-changing
OL,9,Finjuries, the force said.
OL,11,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Allam
OL,14,FBhangoo, who is leading the
OL,15,Finvestigation, said: "As we work
OL,16,Fquickly to identify those responsible,
OL,17,Four thoughts are with Keanu's family
OL,18,Fand friends at this incredibly
OL,19,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
