OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778069461
OL,3,CMan dies after drive-by shooting in
OL,4,CBrixton
OL,6,F"This was a shocking act of violence
OL,7,Fwhich has had a devastating impact on
OL,8,Fthose involved and the local
OL,9,Fcommunity. I want to reassure
OL,10,Fresidents that we are working urgently
OL,11,Fto identify and apprehend those
OL,12,Fresponsible.
OL,14,F"It is vital that anyone who saw what
OL,15,Fhappened, or has any information or
OL,16,Ffootage, comes forward. Even the
OL,17,Fsmallest detail could prove crucial to
OL,18,Four investigation.
